text: They suck. I lost my freaking money.  Lol. Other then that the the older waitress lady is pretty cool. It's clean and they keep all the rif raf out.
The "bartenders" are super rude. I forgot the pricks name but it was if I was wasting his time just ordering cigarettes.

This Dotty's seems to have the rudest employees!  I've been to several Dotty's in Vegas and I won't go to this one anymore.  The bartender never comes around to offer beverages, and when I asked for one he rudely said I have to put $10 in a machine and play it, even after I had been there 20 minutes and put in a $20. Finally I got a Dr Pepper...just ONE can and had been playing for about 2 hours. I won $100 and left without tipping him! (Usually I tip my bartenders  $5)
Loved the place, awesome staff especially Betty!! She makes the place fun and even enjoyable when you win or loss. Great environment.
